Span.Text: Modern productivity tools mean that staff no longer need to go to the office to get their files, access their line of business applications to update their records, or attend meetings.
“Information is accessed and updated directly via mobile devices, avoiding trips to the office to catch up.
As a result, social workers for example, can see 2 or 3 more people per day.”
Barry Wilkinson, ICT Manager, Shropshire Council

“Application of technology is a really important part of our strategy and we've got to make sure we can do the things we really want to do for our local population, and Microsoft is there helping us.”
Sir Robin Wales, Mayor, Newham Borough Council

“I feel immensely proud of the very visible differences we’ve made since implementing Dynamics. We are now responding much faster to customers and helping them with their needs. We’re also delivering accessible, high quality & consistent services and we are being rewarded with record levels of customer satisfaction.”
Liz St Louis, Head of Customer Service & Development, Sunderland City Council
Click to view full case study

Help government workers to do more in less time with solutions that work the way they do across the PC, phone, and browser, via the web or on-premises. They can access the systems they need, whenever they need them, so they don't need to spend time catching up with admin tasks at their desks.

The emergence of video and call conferencing, directly from your desktop, tablet or phone, coupled with Presence, the ability to see at a glance when someone is available, changes the speed at which people communicate. Meetings take less time to arrange, decisions are made more quickly, and people are more effective.

Promote citizen engagement and public safety by enabling constituents to consume and submit information, 24 hours a day. Provide access to readily accessible data, such as weather or traffic, pollution, air quality, emergency dispatch data, or unemployment stats, and make government data more accessible and relevant to citizens through social media.
